{"tid":1987670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「安倍口罩」竟發現污漬、毛髮及破損   日本廠商宣布回收","createTime":"2020-04-24T15:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T09:50:57.000Z","uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b16b7426ec73d2f8d1daf9789a109362614bb141","tid":1987670,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wm7sErP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwm7sErP.jpg&h=67522875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本政府花466億日圓（約台幣131億6千400萬元）買布口罩寄給全國民眾，竟然出現許多瑕疵品。（美聯社） <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本政府向全國每戶家庭發放兩片可重複使用的布口罩，竟被發現部分口罩出現破損等瑕疵，廠商立即宣布回收。首相安倍晉三這個原本就不得人心的計畫，如今留下更大話柄。<br />\n<br />\n彭博資訊報導，收到口罩的民眾反應，口罩不是有髒污就是破損，迫使厚生勞動省命令業者回收並進行品質檢測。伊藤忠商事和Kowa這兩家生產多數口罩的業者已表示，他們會回收尚未發放的口罩。<br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三4月稍早宣布發放布口罩的計畫，盼能解決口罩長期短缺的問題。然而，這項計畫中的口罩在分發前，就成為網路上嘲諷的主題，原因是口罩尺寸太小，以及一戶僅可分到兩片的限制。<br />\n<br />\n這些口罩已名為「安倍口罩」（Abenomask），諧仿日本首相標誌性的安倍經濟學（Abenomics），也有「安倍的口罩」這層意思。這個出自善意卻混亂不堪的示範，已成為安倍處理這場疫情危機不當的最佳寫照。<br />\n<br />\n日本內閣官房長官菅義偉24日說，並不會停止配給口罩。他並表示，這是解決全國口罩短缺「必要的一步」。不過，「由於回收的關係，發放口罩的計畫可能會延後」，政府計劃持續發放口罩，以幫助民眾能「心平靜氣」。<br />\n<br />\n發放口罩的初步計畫已面臨反對的聲浪，毎日新聞在4月18日、19日做的民調顯示，不支持這項計畫的民眾高達68%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4517079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4517079&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=980cd245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4517079</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mainichi.jp/articles/20200424/k00/00m/010/003000c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmainichi.jp%2Farticles%2F20200424%2Fk00%2F00m%2F010%2F003000c&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=f8ace6bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mainichi.jp/articles/20200424/k00/00m/010/003000c</a>"},{"pid":"381e8a560832707968122b413a2bb29dfe7961d0","tid":1987670,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"日本口罩唔係最好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e139137fb08d59328d81651122bd4b9799f2170b","tid":1987670,"uid":69746,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"同支那睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c20a36b4626bce5c4fab53630c6865db03f230","tid":1987670,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"d甩轆野 感覺似港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453163f53f46d14d9466968e6603c65549ed2aad","tid":1987670,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b676da4b6fc36bfa55de0fdcd82be87fc5429cd0","tid":1987670,"uid":50162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"Well this is japan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c269c04b0a1454bd9d820e0739a2cab906a55b","tid":1987670,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b676da4b6fc36bfa55de0fdcd82be87fc5429cd0","tid":1987670,"uid":50162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"Well this is japan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8b8558d3f41475d9bd79792dc467ecab965199","tid":1987670,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;First world&rdquo